    "title": "Opening for Category Manager at Ajio Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Ajio Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Noida operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Ajio Advisory Limited:\nAjio Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ajio Advisory Limited!",
